{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew that hiding, period, there or anywhere else, was just not for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was so terrified that I didn't even remember the hiding place in her room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It never occurred to me even to crawl in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just was frozen, and I knew I could not just wait for them to get me, because every time a doorbell would ring or anytime somebody would knock, I would-- my heart would stop.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I needed to be in control of something, or at least I thought.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this is giving over control, and we sit and wait.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In half an hour?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A week?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- it's a frightful thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then these two girls told me that they were going, because they had received-- because I asked them, how do you know that this is OK and this is on the level?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said-- well, one was very upset that I would even suggest that she wouldn't know what she was doing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She wouldn't hand all that money over to someone, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Friends of hers went and they had-- from a little town in Belgium and from Brussels-- they'd gotten two cards with a code only she and they knew, like everything is fine, you know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Weather's great.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these friends heard again from somebody else before that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this had been going on for a while, so it was absolutely proven.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we made out a code.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Namely, if they arrived in the first village and in Brussels all right, to send me a card saying, everything is fine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wright.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The code name was Wright.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Meanwhile, however, since things were going really, very, very-- a bit dangerous, I must say, more than a bit dangerous.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
